        <mxCell id="vQzI1J59JOSr7eWnOsby-32" value="&quot;Workloads&quot; serves as a central point for application of organizational policies that would be applicable to all workloads.&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;While every folder currently resides underneath the HIGH AW (thus inheriting the organizational policies applied there) creating a central workloads folder allows the platform team to centralize governance and policy application for any policy that should apply to every workload&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;opacity=70;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1970" y="640" width="580" height="100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="vQzI1J59JOSr7eWnOsby-35" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;curved=1;dashed=1;" edge="1" parent="1" source="vQzI1J59JOSr7eWnOsby-34" target="_NAGXmkp-SNP8fUmKOGJ-31">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <Array as="points">
              <mxPoint x="1720" y="800" />
              <mxPoint x="1720" y="640" />
            </Array>
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="vQzI1J59JOSr7eWnOsby-34" value="These folders serve as the &quot;root&quot; for each workloads distinct &quot;sub-org&quot;. All resources deployed by the workload (new folders, projects, IAM bindings / roles, and other resources) are all contained underneath this centralized folder.&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;With IAM not being able to be created at folder level (only at org or project level), workloads must create IAM bindings within their projects.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Upon creation of these workload folders, a GCP RMT (Resource Management Tag) will be assigned to it demarcating the associated workload. (this creation is mandatory and centralized)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Billing accounts can also be created here to tie all workload resources to a central billing account&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;opacity=70;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1860" y="770" width="610" height="190" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="vQzI1J59JOSr7eWnOsby-37" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;curved=1;dashed=1;" edge="1" parent="1" source="vQzI1J59JOSr7eWnOsby-36" target="vQzI1J59JOSr7eWnOsby-6">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="vQzI1J59JOSr7eWnOsby-38" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;curved=1;dashed=1;" edge="1" parent="1" source="vQzI1J59JOSr7eWnOsby-36" target="vQzI1J59JOSr7eWnOsby-16">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <Array as="points">
              <mxPoint x="-390" y="610" />
            </Array>
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="vQzI1J59JOSr7eWnOsby-39" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;curved=1;dashed=1;" edge="1" parent="1" source="vQzI1J59JOSr7eWnOsby-36" target="vQzI1J59JOSr7eWnOsby-15">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <Array as="points">
              <mxPoint x="-390" y="720" />
              <mxPoint x="-40" y="720" />
            </Array>
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="vQzI1J59JOSr7eWnOsby-36" value="These folders / projects may not exist depending on the finalized architecture (not my problem)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;opacity=50;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-470" y="490" width="160" height="70" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="qPJuRytSAQcOQF8F3J8l-1" value="Comment" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry y="150" width="60" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="diJhK68W5ZJjVrEpTWev-1" value="With the platform being ATOd, all central resources utilized by the platform for management and provisioning are located within the FEDRAMP High compliance regime. These centrally managed projects are the few exceptions allowed outside of the HIGH PAB and into the MOD PAB (for sake of management)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;opacity=70;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1940" y="280" width="580" height="100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
