        <mxCell id="9bTvWPntcv-LA0Kk_JXm-12" value="IAM bindings function within three realms of:&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Who&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- What&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Where&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- When&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;The most basic of IAM bindings only focus on the first three, where a principal&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;opacity=60;" vertex="1" parent="0mNAfT45cDVfXiYpLNkF-1">
